{"id":314075,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-数百名上海民众旁听受阻，魏勤、王扣玛/","date":"2013-09-18T17:19:22Z","modified":"2013-09-18T17:19:22Z","title":"维权网 | 数百名上海民众旁听受阻，魏勤、王扣玛当庭获罪（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方子林报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点，上海维权人士魏勤、王扣玛“寻衅滋事”案在闸北区法院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">104</span><span>法庭审理。冯正虎、毛菊华、陆瑛、陆福忠等数百名上海维权人士及民众要求旁听被拒，要求参加旁听的国外使馆官员及记者遭到警察的驱赶，只有当事人的两名家属允许参加旁听。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><span>开庭后，王扣玛高唱着国际歌出庭受审，魏勤也面带微笑，淡定自若。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><span>魏琴的辩护律师尚宝军（北京莫少平律师所务所），王扣玛的辩护律师杨绍刚（上海绍刚律师事务所主任），依据法律与事实，推翻公诉人对魏勤和王扣玛的的诬陷指控，法官多次中止辩护律师的发言。两位律师都为他们的委托人作了无罪辩护。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><span>知名维权人士冯正虎及数百名民众都到现场声援王扣玛、魏勤，要求司法公正。冯正虎撰文《王扣玛在黑监狱旁边祭拜母亲有罪吗？》、《王扣玛是受害者，还是累犯？》，并写信告诉王扣玛、魏勤案件的承办人：“如果错案造成，王扣玛、魏勤会受到无法弥补的伤害，而且承办的检察官、法官也会终身不得安宁，因为错案追责‘终身制’已在试行。”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><span>在庭审进行近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>个小时后，一审法官当庭宣判：王扣玛因“寻衅滋事罪”被判处二年零六个月有期徒刑，魏勤因“寻衅滋事罪”被判处二年零三个月有</span><span>期徒刑</span><span>。王扣玛、魏勤在法庭上坚称自己无罪，将委托律师向上海市第二中级法院依法提起上诉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><span>附：</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><span>上海维权人士魏勤被羁押一年后将出庭受审</span><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_3857.html?spref=tw\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_3857.html?spref=tw</a></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<div>\n<div><span>王扣玛、魏勤的“寻衅滋事罪”案情简要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://woyaolian.info/?p=3350\">http://woyaolian.info/?p=3350</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WKoyinQvZFM/UjnPhPv__8I/AAAAAAAAoXc/GzmtE2bgRQc/s1600/20130917-1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WKoyinQvZFM/UjnPhPv__8I/AAAAAAAAoXc/GzmtE2bgRQc/s1600/20130917-1.JPG\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>感谢上海维权人士舒文提供的现场图片　</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-2lJY0ObdvqQ/UjnPiASvgxI/AAAAAAAAoXo/_pVKbFvSjCs/s1600/20130917-2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-2lJY0ObdvqQ/UjnPiASvgxI/AAAAAAAAoXo/_pVKbFvSjCs/s1600/20130917-2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uSS3zZuCafk/UjnPiBOtxiI/AAAAAAAAoXk/GU5zf187HnE/s1600/20130917-3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uSS3zZuCafk/UjnPiBOtxiI/AAAAAAAAoXk/GU5zf187HnE/s1600/20130917-3.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0zen-UYuQLQ/UjnPjMBEm3I/AAAAAAAAoX0/e2in-X4riQI/s1600/20130917-4.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0zen-UYuQLQ/UjnPjMBEm3I/AAAAAAAAoX0/e2in-X4riQI/s1600/20130917-4.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-L1A9QQMb7Pc/UjnPkOKwK-I/AAAAAAAAoYE/IpnVLUgPSRI/s1600/20130917-5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-L1A9QQMb7Pc/UjnPkOKwK-I/AAAAAAAAoYE/IpnVLUgPSRI/s1600/20130917-5.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--jtFahGDA4M/UjnPkBI-RNI/AAAAAAAAoX4/rI5IOx3hRrs/s1600/20130917-6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--jtFahGDA4M/UjnPkBI-RNI/AAAAAAAAoX4/rI5IOx3hRrs/s1600/20130